{"tid":1107943,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人腸易激都好嚴重？","createTime":"2019-04-15T15:01:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T13:01:01.000Z","uid":201466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bd4937dd16925c9e235536248076bb4667be44c1","tid":1107943,"uid":201466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"有IBS腹瀉型已經三年幾 明明之前咩事都冇<br />\n宜家每日最少痾四至五次 仲要次次都好急 五分鐘內一定要去  所以長途車唔搭得 巴士又唔得<br />\n旅行都冇去 街又少出 就算同frd出街 都每15分鐘就去一次廁所<br />\n就算痾清 個肚都會痛成日 搞到做咩都冇精神<br />\n已經食左一年幾中藥 又試偏方 益生菌 仲戒曬所有奶類 魚生 凍飲 辣野 但都改善不大 <br />\n個人其實冇咩壓力 又早訓 都有IBS<br />\n成日諗自己點解咁失敗 好想死左去就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe026b93b828f555f5351ae2ab29319186efe29e","tid":1107943,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"你睇邊個中醫"},{"pid":"12a05db008b1f82f382efc2ff5c74a7436ec02c9","tid":1107943,"uid":201466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe026b93b828f555f5351ae2ab29319186efe29e","tid":1107943,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"你睇邊個中醫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"農本方旗下既診所"},{"pid":"7245c93ac0b84d4496fa00454945b7e7ed887194","tid":1107943,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12a05db008b1f82f382efc2ff5c74a7436ec02c9","tid":1107943,"uid":201466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe026b93b828f555f5351ae2ab29319186efe29e","tid":1107943,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:09:31.000Z","msg":"你睇邊個中醫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"農本方旗下既診所"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個d一定好廢"},{"pid":"6aa404ef986bc6b80b10da08e2df43145c8542af","tid":1107943,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-15T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"你想係邊睇，我幫你googl